## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="5b1fd-187">다음 예제에서는 한 <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> 속성 중 일부를 설정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5b1fd-187">The following example creates a <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleParameter> and sets some of its properties.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
